Poland ' s Krotoszyn eyes PLN 5 - 6 mln munibond issue . The town of Krotoszyn , located in western Poland , plans to privately place municipal bonds worth 5 - 6 million zlotys around the middle of the year after it finds an issue agent , a city official said on Thursday . " We expect the issue to take place in June or July and we target the amount of 5 - 6 million zlotys , " Lucyna Bogdanska , an official from Krotoszyn ' s promotion department told Reuters . Bogdanska said Krotoszyn would likely choose the agent of the issue by the end of March . The cash would be spent on creating a rehabilition centre in the city . - - Wojciech Moskwa + 48 22 653 9700 
